116void
117isc_crc64_init(uint64_t *crc) {
118 REQUIRE(crc != NULL);
119
120 *crc = 0xffffffffffffffffULL;
121}
122
123void
124isc_crc64_update(uint64_t *crc, const void *data, size_t len) {
125 const unsigned char *p = data;
126 int i;
127
128 REQUIRE(crc != NULL);
129 REQUIRE(data != NULL);
130
131 while (len-- > 0U) {
132 i = ((int) (*crc >> 56) ^ *p++) & 0xff;
133 *crc = crc64_table[i] ^ (*crc << 8);
134 }
135}
136
137
138void
139isc_crc64_final(uint64_t *crc) {
140 REQUIRE(crc != NULL);
141
142 *crc ^= 0xffffffffffffffffULL;
143}
